summary: Beautiful Imperial (Thief), with quite a few skills maxed out.
descriptionHtml:
Beautiful Imperial, with quite a few skills maxed out.
Originally a thief, but here are things I have finished with her...

~ All Dark Brotherhood Quests
~ Half-Way Done with Thieves Guild
~ Started Main Quest, most of it incomplete so you can do most of it yourself.
~ Lots of Spells

Something To keep in mind, this save file has a lot of files that have been modded, so in order to experience the full effects of this character I recommend you download these extra mods:
~ Triss Armor Retexture
http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=4708
~ Tytanis
http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=1601
~ Coolsims Hair Pack
http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=3809
